<tab><cl=F0F010>HARON<cl=A2A2A2><br><br>
<tab>Players with bad<l="hts:\\language\i_charact.hts">karma<\l> after their death can reincarnate on Charon.  Its landscape is severely mutilated, almost a wasteland, that is nearly impassable and densely populated with monsters. Escaping from Charon is quite a difficult task, although it is not impossible.<br>
